data.description: *PRICE REDUCED!!* What an opportunity!  Welcome to this attractive Kingswood model Townhome in the lovely NE community of Village North.  One of the larger models, this two story home features a welcoming and comfortable living room with a wood burning fireplace.  The kitchen and dining room arrangement is practical and efficient.  And throughout the home there's storage galore!  The primary bedroom downstairs is secluded and expansive with an en suite bathroom, and sliding glass doors overlook the patio. A half bath is conveniently located along the hallway for guests.  Lots of natural light as more sliding glass doors lead to the large, enclosed patio which is half roofed over, and half al fresco for the perfect mix of sun and shade.  Walk through the gate from the patio and you are literally just steps away from the community pool.   The 2 bedrooms upstairs are also oversized and incorporate a Jack and Jill bathroom.  The floor in the one car garage is freshly painted and has built in shelving.  The low monthly HOA includes lawn care, pool maintenance and common grounds maintenance.  Great location, convenient to downtown, shopping, dining, grocery shopping and health care services.
